    <title>Alternate Authentication Endpoints</title>
    <para> You can use the current Cloud Identity authentication endpoints with earlier versions of
        the API. All versions of the API, including legacy Identity contracts, are available if you
        authenticate at a current endpoint and specify an API version.  Whichever version of the API
        you choose, you must use the endpoint designated for your US-based or UK-based
        account.</para>
